Class ProviderAssocAbstract

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.hudup.core.data.ProviderAssocAbstract
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    AutoCloseable, ProviderAssoc

    public abstract class ProviderAssocAbstract
extends java.lang.Object
implements ProviderAssoc
    This abstract class implements partially the ProviderAssoc interface. It add the internal configuration config for ProviderAssoc. Note, ProviderAssoc assists the provider specified by interface Provider to performs read-write operations.
